# 🌿 Stoner4TheRecord
# Production Platform & Digital Broadcasting Ecosystem
## Version 2.0

---

# Vision

Stoner4TheRecord is more than a website.

It is an all-in-one broadcasting platform that combines:

- Television Studio
- Radio Station
- Production Control Room
- Podcast Network
- Live Event Platform
- Gaming Platform
- Community Platform
- Media Library

The website itself powers the entire production.

There are no third-party production tools required for day-to-day broadcasting.

Everything happens from within the Stoner4TheRecord platform.

---

# Three Core Platforms

## 🌐 Website

The public-facing broadcast station.

Used for:

- Watching live broadcasts
- Listening live
- Community chat
- Episode archive
- Merchandise
- Sponsors
- DJ profiles
- Shows
- Schedules
- Media library

---

## 📱 Mobile App

The mobile app is the viewer companion.

It is **NOT** designed to watch the broadcast as its primary purpose.

Instead it allows viewers to interact with the broadcast in real time.

Features include:

- Game Cards
- Trivia Answers
- Bingo Cards
- Live Voting
- Song Requests
- Polls
- Giveaways
- Chat
- Push Notifications
- QR Code Scanner
- Community
- Rewards
- Digital Membership Card

The app becomes the audience's controller.

---

## 🎬 Production Studio

A completely separate production dashboard.

Only accessible to authorized staff.

Runs the entire broadcast.

---

# Production Dashboard

The production dashboard is the control room.

Every department logs into their own workstation.

No one shares accounts.

Each user only sees the controls they need.

