# Multi-User Broadcasting

The system supports simultaneous logins.

Example:

Executive Producer

Host

DJ

Sound Engineer

Graphics

Lighting

Camera 1

Camera 2

Camera 3

Game Master

Moderator

Sponsor Coordinator

