# Ultimate Goal

Stoner4TheRecord is designed as a complete digital broadcasting ecosystem.

The website serves as the network.

The production dashboard serves as the television control room.

The mobile app serves as the audience's interactive companion.

Every broadcast, game, recording, playlist, and community interaction lives within a single unified platform, allowing creators, staff, sponsors, DJs, hosts, and viewers to participate together in one seamless entertainment experience.
